text:
A greatful and legendary Cross-collab ever. :_きゅん:
Also the first Rushia-daitenshi's Cross-collab ever. :_るんるん:
No BGM at intro due to collab and also because intro's video was prepared without music at January 2020.

The 5 Holomembers and the 5 2434's members made a good job. :_ハート:

It's surprising the good ending at the last game (4th Round)
But anyway, everyone... Wait... What I'm thinking... Some of Holomembers and Nijimembers are part of a Dream Team which I'm making... Well, someone would ask me about that at Twitter. 😉

And... Moments like this cross-collab needs to be repeated... Maybe the same people, or other people... :_ハート:

I have an idea, but I don't know if would result... Rushia would need to make collabs with unknown vtubers. Let's write at Mashimaro 🥰

Yes... :_きゅん: Well... Forget my Yabai-esque idea, please
